				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Sarik looks like a giant wolf,  except,  he likes all Druids.  Sarik responds to hails only when you are a druid...  This is what he says...<BR>
<BR>
You say,  &quot;Hail Sarik the Fang&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says, &quot;Well hello there young druid.  Have you been to the Tunarian Tree?  Please visit our greatest leader,  Tunare.&quot;<BR>
You say,  &quot;Who is Tunare?&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says, &quot;Tunare is the ruler of this plane.  I must suggest you kill other people who tries to kill her.&quot;<BR>
You say,  &quot;Other people?&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says, &quot;Yes.  People have tried to kill her but have failed.  Of course,  people are no match for her...&quot;<BR>
You say, &quot;People?&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says, &quot;We druids possess powerful magic...  Tunare has given us druids those type of magic.  She is our Druidic God.&quot;<BR>
You say,  &quot;Powerful magic?&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says,  &quot;Yes.  Powerful magic.  There are four scrolls hidden within this plane.  Some creatures or other type of races are enemies to this plane.  Please kill them.  Some of the may have the scroll of [Fire],  [Ice],  [Lightning] and [Wind].  Are you willing to help?&quot;<BR>
You say,  &quot;I am willing to help.&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says,  &quot;You are the kindest druid I have met.  Please take this box.  Collect all four scrolls and you shall recieve the powerful magic from Tunare.  I will notify her to give me that spell to give to you.  Please be careful on your journey and bring me those scrolls.  They have powerful curses.&quot;<BR>
You say,  &quot;Powerful curses?&quot;<BR>
Sarik the Fang says,  &quot;Powerful curses that those scrolls possess can kill anyone instantly.  If YOU use that on me,  Tunare,  Protector of the Glades or the Keeper of the Glades,  I must kill you for what you have done.  Please don't use the curse for evil purposes.&quot;<BR>
<BR>
Sarik the Fang is the druidic wolf who asks druids only to help Tunare and himself to get the four scrolls.  They are hard to get.  I only found the Wind scroll and the Fire scroll.  If you know where the other scrolls are,  please give more imformations about it.  I would appreciate it.  I am a level 59 druid on the server of Tunare,  name is Serovus Manastrife.  If you are willing to help me,  please send me email to &quot; Druidsero83475@aol.com &quot;.  You will recieve a huge amount of reward from me in the game.  (10000pp for each scroll).  These scrolls are just magic/lore items FYI...  =)  Thank you for your time.  (One more thing,  if your faction is real low with druidians,  Sarik the Fang will not respond to you at all.  If he doesn't respond to you,  that means your factions are low with druids...  And yes,  druids can talk to him if you worship Tunare and have HIGH factions.
